=Description=

"Mas Els Gorgs is a Laboratory for Experimental Living in the Alta Garrotxa Natural Park. We're an international group of people living in an old cement quarry. Our doing springs naturally from the core of our authentic being and expresses rather than seeks openness and love. For us it is all about being experimental, gardening, building, maintaining, developing, playing local, thinking glocal."
